  "title": "Urgent!! Class 3 Driver",
  "description": "<p><strong>Part Time Delivery min $120 per day</strong></p><p>Part Time Class 3 Van Delivery Driver (now till eve of CNY)</p><ul><li>Check, handle and deliver cartons of goods</li><li>Deliver orders to customers’ doorstep / offices</li><li>Maintain good relationship with customers</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements</strong></p><p>1. Possess valid Singapore Class 3 driving license with at least 1 year of driving experience</p><p>2. No traffic violation records</p><p>3. Company vehicle will be allocated to you for the delivery work. Candidate with vehicle are open to apply</p><p>4. Able to commit 8 to 12 hours of delivery per day</p><p>5. Able to carry and move <strong>non Halal goods</strong> (up to 20kg/ctn) with trolley</p><p>6. Able to speak and read English</p><p>7. Able to know how to use navigation, preferably familiar with Singapore routes or good with maps and directions</p>",
